Casey, 1918: 91. Type locality: &quot;Washington State&quot; (original citation). Lectotype (♂), designated by Lindroth (1975: 120), in USNM [# 36951]. Synonymy established, under the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Casey" authorityYear="1918" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="399" pageNumber="400" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="imperitum">
